(44, 13, 40, 39, 3, 2, 2, 'which is spoken of in the prophets', 'Judgment and Refinement Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of judgment and purification. Acts 13:40 warns of consequences foretold by the prophets, while Malachi 3:2 speaks of the refining process associated with the coming of the Lord.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
