(44, 13, 41, 60, 4, 17, 17, 'ye shall in no wise believe', 'Judgment and Unbelief Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of judgment beginning with those who have received the message, as seen in both passages. Acts 13:41 warns of disbelief leading to perishing, while 1 Peter 4:17 emphasizes judgment starting at the house of God.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
